{{See also|Category:Legendary creatures in works of fiction}}
{{Commons category|Fantasy creatures}}

There are several different types of fantasy creatures ranging from the athropinians to the zophians.
The creatures were believe to be real at one point in time but were recently discovered to be false statements.

